                    <li><strong>Immediate action:</strong> Review individual ad performance within this ad set â€” pause any ads below 2.5x ROAS</li>
                    <li><strong>Creative test:</strong> Reframe remaining Dec products with "gift for her" or "treat yourself" messaging</li>
                    <li><strong>Learning for 2026:</strong> December Week 1 launches need gift-oriented creative from day one, not standard "new arrivals" positioning</li>
                </ul>
