                        <li>Scale Weekly Arrivals to $3,500/day during peak window</li>
                        <li>Feature proven categories: sweaters, jackets, plaid patterns</li>
                        <li>Launch "Fall Favorites" collection campaign</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="strategy-box">
                <strong>October Peak Window Scaling Protocol:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Oct 1-15 (Ramp Phase):</strong>
                        <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 5px;">
                            <li>Increase Weekly Arrivals budget from $1,200/day to $2,000/day (+67%)</li>
                            <li>Priority products: Sweaters, quilted jackets, plaid prints (proven 7-9x ROAS winners)</li>
                            <li>Monitor ROAS daily â€” if above 4.5x after 7 days, proceed to full scale</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li><strong>Oct 16-Nov 15 (Peak Phase):</strong>
                        <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 5px;">
                            <li>Scale Weekly Arrivals to $3,500/day (max recommended for account size)</li>
                            <li>Keep winning ad sets from Oct running alongside new weekly launches</li>
                            <li>Exception: If any ad set drops below 3.5x ROAS for 5 days, reduce budget 50%</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li><strong>"Fall Favorites" Collection Campaign ($5K budget):</strong>
                        <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 5px;">
                            <li>Create dedicated campaign featuring top 10 products from Sept-Oct Weekly Arrivals</li>
                            <li>Carousel format showing "Customer Favorites" social proof angle</li>
                            <li>Target: Engaged non-purchasers who viewed products but didn't buy</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="action-item priority-medium">
                <div class="action-title">3. Holiday Gift Campaign (Dec 1-20)</div>
                <div class="action-desc">
                    <ul>
                        <li>Launch "Gift Guide" campaign targeting gift-givers</li>
                        <li>Feature giftable items: accessories, gift sets, gift cards</li>
                        <li>Test "Treat Yourself" self-gifting angle</li>
                        <li>Implement shipping cutoff urgency messaging</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

