        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2>Risk Factors & Mitigations</h2>
                <p class="subtitle">Proactive Planning for Potential Challenges</p>
            </div>

            <div class="three-column">
                <div class="action-item priority-high">
                    <div class="action-title">âš ï¸ CPM Inflation</div>
                    <div class="action-desc">
                        <strong>Risk:</strong> Meta CPMs rise 15-20% industry-wide<br><br>
                        <strong>Mitigation:</strong>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Build larger warm audiences</li>
                            <li>Invest in creative quality</li>
                            <li>Maintain LTV:CAC buffer</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="action-item priority-medium">
                    <div class="action-title">âš ï¸ Creative Fatigue</div>
                    <div class="action-desc">
                        <strong>Risk:</strong> Top performers decline after 4-6 weeks<br><br>
                        <strong>Mitigation:</strong>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Weekly fresh creative from arrivals</li>
                            <li>Monthly testing budget</li>
                            <li>Q3 creative bank for Q4</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="action-item priority-medium">
                    <div class="action-title">âš ï¸ Inventory Constraints</div>
                    <div class="action-desc">
                        <strong>Risk:</strong> Best sellers sell out before ad optimization<br><br>
                        <strong>Mitigation:</strong>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Coordinate ads with inventory</li>
                            <li>Auto-pause triggers for low stock</li>
                            <li>"Back in stock" remarketing</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="alert-box">
                <strong style="color: #991b1b;">Platform Risk:</strong> Meta algorithm changes could impact Advantage+ campaign performance. Mitigation: Maintain 15% budget in manual CBO campaigns as a hedge, and stay current with Meta's best practices and beta features.
            </div>
